values: Riley at 2 months

So I was just siting at school on the computer and I remembered that I even had this thing :P
So how is Megan?  WAAAAAAAAAY too pregnant.  38 weeks on thursday...I am so miserable and I hurt more and more every day, I just want this whole part of being a mom to be over with.  Besides that...well there really is nothing besides that.  We finished the nursery about 2-3 weeks ago and it is SOOOOO cute.  The ceiling is blue, 2 walls are yellow and two walls are green.   I didnt really want a theme because there was really nothing that I liked.  I had to register at diff places and it seemed like everywhere you looked for bedding, it was either winnie the pooh or farm animals, neither of which I wanted so we just stuck with doing colors. I have gained 30lbs but you cannot really tell that I have gained that much...all of the weight has gone straight to my ass, but since my belly is so huge now it kinda even outs the ass...I had a dream last night though that I had the baby and afterwards I was really concerned about all of the weight that I had gained because I was no longer pregnant and I just looked fat.

I am still in my microbiology class and English.  I have had 3 tests in micro... 2A's and 1B.  The B kinda sucked but what can ya do?  I didnt study for it like I should have.

I am not sure if I already said that I had been excepted into the nursing program, but I have...It starts June 6th, Riley wont even be 2 months, but we will figure things out.  luckily for the summer the class is only 2 days a week , 4 hours a day, and it does not last the entire summer.
anyhoo I suppose I should get started on what I came here for... to work on my english paper.

http://www.babycenter.com/mybabycenter/130.html?scid=mbtw_preg31:20060130:0:0:0

Things are going good right now.
We still have not gotten the nursery ready but we do have everything we need to do it.  We are just slow to get things done.
I had the worse kidney stone the other day...They gave me 3 or 4 shots of morphine and a vicadin and It still hurt REALLY bad...they were about to wheel me into surgery to implant a stint in my ureter, but right as they came to get me, I passed it! yay!  it was HUGE! it came out in a big ol blood clot and it was 4mm.  I will find out on thursday what it causing me to get these...this was my 2nd one since I became pregnant.  Hopefully I do not get anymore.  My belly is getting huge...I should post a picture but I forgot my disk that has them on it...maybe I will try sometime tonight or tomorrow night when Kari is at work because there is internet access up there.
Anyhoo, I have gained 24 lbs...They say that is the perect wieght for me to gain at the point that I am at, and that 35 shold be the max by the time he is born.  They say since I am going to breastfeed that I should loose most of the weight really quickly...I hope that is the case.  My butt is HUGE, Kari says I have a mommy's butt :P
Oh well I should do some homework.

Last night I was laying in bed and I had my fingers pressed against the side of my belly.  I was able to feeling him moving his foot up and down the side of my uterus, it was CRAZY, the way it felt and the fact that I was even able to identify what part of him I was feeling.  At one point it kind of tickled and hurt at the same time and it made me jump. I was neat though.
I jsut wrote an awful paper for english.  I suck at writing.  I am better at classes that I have to memorize stuff for.  I am more of a black or white person I guess.

http://www.babycenter.com/mybabycenter/127.html?scid=mbtw_preg28:20060109:0:0:0

sheesh, only 12 more weeks and I will have my little boy :P
I cannot wait to see him.

Microbiology is very cool, I like it WAY more than physiology.
anyhoo, I am in the library, I think I will go study for a while.

mmm...my belly is getting big.
I have gained 15 lbs so far, my doctor says that I am right on track as far as weight goes...I was PRAYING that I would not me one of those pregnant women who claim they are eating for two and gain 50lbs.  I am not sure if I already put this in here, but we decided on a name. 
Riley Osten Pele ( with a little mark above the first e) Karisson (with a mark above the a)  That is how they do last names in Iceland, and since our baby is half viking, we decided that we would follow that tradition.  
He moves all the time.  You can tell he is starting to get crowded in tehre because instead of feeling pokes and prods, I feel his entire body move, sometimes I can feel his hand or leg just run across my abdomen. Its very neat.
I am taking 3 classes this semester, Developmental Psych, English and Microbiology.  When the baby is born I will only be in Micro so that will be nice.  That will be for about a month or two, then I have two weeks off and Then I start the nursing program.  Next summer I will be a LPN and the following a RN.  VERY exciting.

Havent updated for a while.
This semester is almost over...THANK GOD!  It has been the semester from hell.
I received my letter of acceptance into the nursing program last week, so by next summer I  will be a LPN, and the following a RN.  :D YAY!

All Riley does these days is kick.  He kicks really hard and its fun :P  My mom bought us a crib, dresser and changing table which we got in the mail a few nights ago and I now have blisters all over my hands because I spent all night building them.  Then I laid Gracie in them and pretended she was my baby :)  it was fun, but she no likey it.

Life is going pretty well, besides money problems I can not complain.  Kari will be going back to work as soon as classes end next week, so we should be better off then.

I should go do what I came to school for.

http://i33.photobucket.com/albums/d69/mentalerror/megan.jpg

first pic is just the back of his head and a arm
second pic is of his profile

ITS A BOY!!!! :P
Gosh the ultrasound was so awesome today.  We saw his little feet and hands and fingers, in one of the pictures you can count his fingers, its very cool.  We have pictures of his profile, of his little butt and arms and legs. so freakin cool.  at one point in the ultrasound he looked like he was boxing. :D  He does kick all the time.
We will name him Riley.  we have not thought of middle names yet.

I am not sure if I posted this already, but Kari took an acting class this semester and will be performing in 4 skits Friday and Saturday night in the theater at school, it will be fun.  HOWEVER I am SUPER over having to be stuck at school while they all practice for 4 hours.  I am stuck right now.
My baby is kicking.
Uhm...I am avoiding working on my physiology homework.
I am hungry and could go for a big fat cheeseburger.
and onion rings.
and a milkshake.
mmm...
My mom sent me a new baby book in the mail, which I got today...those are fun.
I think I convinced myself to go to A&W.

Life is OK.  We finally got a new roof.  That is the best thing that has happened to us in a long time.  School still sucks...5 more weeks and it is over! YAY!
3 days until we find out if we are having a boy or a girl.  SO EXCITING!!! Then next tuesday we get my blood results back...but they said if anything came back abnormal they would give us a call, and that was 2 or 3 weeks ago, so I guess that means the baby is OK, even though the results are only about 85 percent accurate.  Anyhoo, i will update on thursday :)

Soooo I got a few kidney stones on Friday night.  Horrible horrible.  I had to go to the emergency room, and I was so freaked out about taking any drugs, but they gave me morphine and said that it was safe for my baby.  When I got home at about 1am, I was beat so I laid down...and my baby must have been STONED because I never have felt it move the way it was moving that night.  Usually it is just little taps, but I swear I felt the entire body do a flip, for like 3 minutes.  It was very cool. :D  Now that I have felt it move and kick though, I am a nervous wreck when I have not felt it move for a while.  I suppose that is normal though.

I will find out what we are having Nov. 17th.   WooHoo!

I have a exam in physiology in a little over a hour... not looking forward to it.

they say not to wear pantyhose while pregnant.
what is a girl to do?

I am 16 weeks.
I felt my baby kick on Friday evening.  it was AWESOME!  It kicks really hard for being so tiny.  it feels like popcorn....just not so fast, like when its almost all done popping and you here a pop every 30 secs.  anyhoo it is amazing.  when i felt it, it made this pregnancy thing feel SO different.  I feel so different about this whole experience.  :P

I am 15 weeks 3 days :P
I have an appointment tomorrow morning, I look forward to these everyday that I do not have one.

Life is kinda blah right now.  I have been feeling really depressed.  I never realized how many people stop calling you when you get pregnant.  Its like all of a sudden you have a disease. HELLO, I am pregnant not handicapped.  I can still go out and have fun WITHOUT drinking.  What do I expect though?  All of my friends are alcoholics anyway.  I can not wait to start my classes.  I will meet people who have things in common with me... Like having a parasite growing inside them. :P haha, j/k.
Seriously though, My mom is like the only person that calls me these days.  Joni calls me everyonce in a while, but I think it is just to make me feel better...I do no not think she REALLY wants to parade around town with a pregnant, girl.

School SUCKS this semester. physiology is SO boring.  I can not wait for it to be over.  I am taking Microbiology next semester, I hear that is way more interesting. 

I think ill go stab myself in the face now.

I have let myself get so far behind this semester.  I have a C in Physiology, and that REALLY blows.  If I straighten up now I will get out of this class with a B, but that is still pretty depressing because it is going to bring my GPA back down below a 3.5 ... I think anyways.  I have a test I need to study for tonight and then I am going to straighten up.  I cannot afford to do bad...especially now. 
I have been at school since 11 and I will not get out of here until 8... I love my life :P 

no

WELP
On thursday, according to my ultrasound, I will be starting my 2nd trimester...woohoo!
School sucks, I am being such a slacker this semester, I really need to get on the ball. My eye stings and my elbow itches.... and that is all

We went and did our ultra sound yesterday.  IT WAS SO AWESOME! At one point, I know it was just floating around, but it looked like it was doing jumping jacks and you could see of its limbs at the same time.  They said that I am exactly 10 weeks along and that my due date is April 13th.  On Thursday it will no longer be called an embryo, it will be called  fetus...all that means is that the baby has all the organs it needs to live, they just need to mature now. :P  If I can find a place to scan the ultra sound pics, I will put them on here.

I have  sty in my eye and it hurts like hell.  I can barely blink it is so sore.
SO I am roughly 8 weeks along now.  If that is true, then the little fingers and toes are formed :P  I will find out soon enough exactly how far along I am.  Thats exciting.

I have a huge physiology test tomorrow... I think I am screwed.  I will be pulling an all nighter tonight.  Fun times

We are going to have a baby.
It only took me 3 at home tests and two visits to the doctor to be able to say that.

Life is great.  I was in a rut for about a week.  I have developed some nasty rash on my back and chest that has been there for almost a month now.  I am going to a dermatologist on Thursday to get it checked out.  I have gained 10 pounds, but I hope that now I am back in school, it will not be that hard to drop.  I have been sleeping a lot and have been very moody BUT 
Today was my first day back in classes and it was just what I needed.  I feel 100% better now.  It is amazing how that works.  Physiology seems like it is going to be tough, but I think I am falling in love with science.

Have been doing nothing but working these days.  School starts back up next Monday and I am very excited about that.  I am taking Human physiology, Sociology for the modern family, CNA and Mixed Media.  Life is slow when I am not in school.
I made a new friend at work.  Her name is Joni.  She just moved here 2 months ago, she likes to play pool and she likes minesweeper, my kind of girl :P
Kari and I got our entire garage cleaned out, and if you had seen it before, you would have known what a job that was.  It took a week, but it looks really nice, and for some reason after it was finished, the place seemed more like home.
I have no complaints other than the people I work for have turned out to be bigger assholes than I was warned about.  OH WELL

I went on a diet.  I went from 124 to 133 in a little less than two weeks.  I am back down to 129 but I want to reach 120 this time.  I swore off fast ffod forever except for the occasional pizza from work cuz that stuff is yummy.  I have been eating salads and yogurt for te last two days.  Tonight I think I am going to have Kari make me some fish.
I am going to take a weigh lifting class this coming semester, I want to get all buff n shit.

I have been drinking entirely too much this past week or so.  I like to stay after work and have a few drinks with my co workers, but then almost always, we go out after the place closes and I end up really wasted.  I have made a lot of new friends at work.  they are all really awesome people, including the owners, which is nice.  The one bar tender Nancy is a radio voice on 92.1 and she dedicated Tom Petty's American girls to me the night before last.... she said this is to Megan, you frigging retard. Haha, you had to be there.
A girl from South Dakota works there also, she and her boyfriend moved here about a month ago because he got a job at the hospital, other than that, they hate it here.  
I talked to this boy from palmer last night.  I am pretty sure I am going to palmer, but most likely east or west.

been busy these days.  all my time is tied up in either studying or working.  i am doing the waitress thing now and I like it a lot, they actually make pretty good money for not needing an education.  i am like a chameleon at work and so everyone I wait on thinks i am just grand.  in fact everyone at work thinks I am great too.  I decided that pretending to be nice helps me to get my way almost 99% of the time, I could get used to that.

i have  a muscle practical tomorrow and I am not completely prepared for it, I should get home and study seeing that i have lees than 12 hours.

I got my grades today...
Sociology  A-
Chemistry A
Keyboarding A
so my grade point average right now is 3.89 :)
I am satisfied with that
waiting to take one of my finals.  I have one more tomorrow and then the semester is over and I have a month before my summer class starts.  very exciting!

this is my last week of the spring semester.  I have a month off and then I start the summer semester... anatomy...i will have no life for 8 weeks.  I am going to visit my Grandma on the 27th, AI can not wait to see her, she is wonderful.  She is making me a quilt right now...and I know that makes her seem like a boring old lady who knits all the time.  She is awesome thought.  she has a salty mouth and likes to talk about sex... its kinda disturbing but funny too.
I am excited about seeing my sister, and I will most likely spend one night with my dad, just becasue I will feel bad if I dont.

I am on pain meds because of my accident, so I have been constanley stoned :)

I was in my first car accident today.  This girl ran a stop sign, and I slammed into her.  When I got out of the car, I immediatley went over to make sure everyone was OK, and there she was, sitting there crying with two babies in the back seat...she was not even checking on them.  She was under 18, no license, no insurance, and the front of my truck is a mess. Then she left after I got her info, and I called the police becasue I did not know hwta else to do...to bad I have no idea what happens next.  My head hurts.

i am so fucking tired of dealing with the fasfa shit, it is really starting to get old... this is seriously the most stressful part of going to school when you are poor, it would be so much easier if I could just pay in cash.

I am doing this job for my Art teacher now.  I have to go and spend a 24 hour period with his 93 year old mother in law, getting paid 8 dollars an hour tax free... I think thats great. :P  I have nothing better to do, I get to eat, sleep, shower and study all I want :D  I go over there tomorrow at 6, and stay till 6 the next day.

I have SO many bills to pay it is not even funny, and i only have about 50 dollars.  SUCKS to be ME.

I will make 30 today when I go stand nakid in front of young boys who have never seen a nakid chick besides the ones in movies, and the magazines that they steal from their dads.  

I drew a big picture of a uterus on my chest last night and it took me 30 minutes to scrub it off of me...I am raw.

i will be rich
i promis you that, and everyone that has helped us thorugh this rough time will get an all paid for vacation, just to show how rich i am... you all should snd me money, and I will be nice to you too when I am rich :P

I am going to be nakid in front of lots of people tomorrow.  LUCKY ME

doing nothing more than killing time...that I should be using to figure out how I am going to pay all the bills coming up in the next three days... ha-ha I suck.
I am going swimming tonight at the Hotel that Kari is working at; I will have the whole thing to myself.  Yippee, I love to swim and have not done so for such a long time that I might have forgotten how to. or not.
I had a chemistry test the other day... one that I thought for sure I was going to bomb, but I ended up getting a B... a low B but better than what I thought I was going to get.  I have a 89.4 in the class, that is really lame, but I will get out of there with an A, I have no doubt in my mind.
I am fucking STARVING

Waiting for Kari to get out o her meeting is driving me mad.  This will be the third time I have updated today, and I am starting to have flash backs to the days when I did nothing more than stay drunk, stoned, and update my journal all day. 
I will go out and smoke...pretend that I have a life and wait until I can pick Kari up from that damn meeting...Only so I can go home, clean and help her study for that damn bone practical she has on Thursday.  My life is grand.

I just updated...BUT...

I was walking downt he hallway just a few minutes ago, to take Kari to a meeting and we walked past the art gallery... AND TO MY SURPRISE... there are two nakid pantings/drawings of me in there.  Because I do the nude modeling for the class, and I know what my boobs look like and my belly button ring, I am very confident when I say that the paintings/drawings of the nakid body are mine.  

THAT IS WICKED :D  I think I am going to ask the guy if I can buy one, or I might just bring my camera tomorrow and take pictures.

I wish I had a clue.

Last week... Or maybe two weeks ago, Kari and I went out with Missy and JD.  It was weird being aroudn Missy because after that shit she pulled my last week at Hope Haven, I had basically written her off.  I think because I still talked to JD that drove her crazy.  HaHa, Like I would ever have anything to do with him other than be friends.  I like thin people.  That is so vein.

My dad called me on Easter after looking at an Email that I had sent my grandma.  He wants to buy that picture that I painted of that lady ... I posted it on my jounal a while ago...I think it is still there.  I dunno if I will let him have it...he is a jerk and I do not know if I want to give him what he wants.  I want to denie him shit, like he has done to me.

It is in the 70's today.  This makes me very happy.  Winter and snow brings me down after a few weeks, althought I must admit that I look better in winter cloths than I do in summer cloths.  such is my luck.  I would say it is because my legs are so pale and pastie.  If I could wear my pantyhose in the summer with my shorts, I would be sexy :P... I guess that I will just wear skirts and dresses all summer, so that i have an excuse.

I have been waiting for spring break to b over, It was boring...I guess I am not good at finding things to do with my time.
First day back was supposed to be a happy day, yet I have a pounding headache and can barely keep my head up.  I went to look at Karis work last night and was told that Ic ould come swimming anytime I want when she is working, that is happy news, I love to swim...covered completely that is.  I used to be self conscious becuase of my wieght, and I wold not let anyone see me in a sui, but now I am worried about how pale I am.  It is icky.  Last night when we went to the grochery store, we looked at our selves in the video camera, and i was like a ghost.  Being almost translucent is some kind of punishment.  Maybe I will just start wearing pantyhose with my swimming suit.  That would be funny

have not been doing much these days.
I am on spring break and nothing could be more boring.  Ive cleaned house over and over just hoping to find something that I have not seen in a while.  School starts back on monday, I could not be anymore excited.  Kari is going to work tonight, and I think that i will get drunk and take pictures...and maybe post them sometime this week.
My dad is a bastard, nothing new, and he is avoiding my calls right now, because he knows I want something...I want his financial info, and he still has not sent it to me
asshole

I haven't read this thing for what seems like forever.  I have been super busy with school and finding a new job.  I found one, as a companion.  Kari got hired at two places today.  At a place where she helps take care of the mentally disabled and one as a night clerk at a hotel.  This means that i will have to do all the house work now, but that is not  a problem I guess, at least we can pay our bills again.
I signed up for an Anatomy class this summer.  That is the only class I will take.  This fall I will be taking Developmental Psych, Physiology, a CNA class and a sociology class... that is a FULL load concidering that Physiology is one of the hardest classes given at this school, besides Anatomy ( not that one I am taking, the one Kari is in now)
I went and got my eyes checked today, seems as thought I am far sighted and I am going to need to get glasses.  Lucky me, but seriously, I am kinda happy about it because I have been having so many headaches these last few months, and it is because my right eye is giving me so many problems.
Kari looks really hot today and everyone has been saying how hot HE is
I agree, very sexy. we are a cute ass couple, what can I say?

I am wearing pantyhose today, have been for the last week.  I do not like to weat underware with them, so my pubic hair hurts at the end of the day, I am sure everyone wanted to hear about that.  I shaved today :P

we are trying to quit smoking and it sucks
we have been at each others throat the entire day

we are not really concerned with our health, its basically that we are to poor to support our habit

haha, we are lame.

I am in the library and there are two really obnoxious girls in here talking on their cells phones as loud as they can, because they are cool that way
I want to run their heads in to the wall.  yep yep

I applied for a few jobs today, i need some money so i can support my cig and milk habit

I dropped my english class on friday, the asshole of a teacher almost made me cry, and I am like wtf? this is not highschool, so why do i feel like it is?  Oh well, Kari and I do not have a phone anymore, thats what happens when you are po'
One of these days, things will be great, after we are all through with school that is.  
My nails are getting long again... This gu fez is trying to teach me to play guitar, but I am reluctant because my hands never looked so good and I dont want to cut my nails off :/
I am so shallow sometimes.
I have a chemistry test next wednesday... andyea
I am going to go down to the boat today and see if I can get a job as a casino gambler today, that would be a pretty cool job... even though most of the people that work down there are fugly as hell, including one chick that sits next to me in my chemisty class and talks to me all the time and she is a complete moron, she is nasty and she wants to bea  nurse but she will never make it because she is to fucking stupid.
I wish i knew why I went on that rant.
I gained like 3 pounds over the weekend, for some reason i could not stop eating. it was rediculous.
I have having pains in my left lung today, i wonder what it is from, maybe i should quit smoking.
oh well

I figured out exactly how my program works.  In order to get into the Mortuary Science programm, I have to complete 4 more classes...but I have two semesters to finish them because the program does not start until the Fall, which is next semester and I have to finish those pre reqs.  Oh well this means i get to take 4 classes that I do not need but I would like to take, like sociology for the family, enviormental science, US government and uhmm... probably abnormal psych.  I love school :D

I ended up getting a B on my chemistry exam... I was really upset about this because I was so sure that I was going to get an A, she put up the grades in the class though, ( without names ) and 4 people got an A, 4 people got a B, 11 people got a C, 2 people got a D and 2 people got a F... so when I saw that, I did not feel that bad about my B, but I will get an A on the next test.  My goal is to get a higher grade than Kari got in this class, which was a B, but on her first test she got a C... so far I am doing better :P

I wrote the first draft of my new paper for English, it's a Persuation paper... I think this one is going to be very good.

Anyhoo
